Transcription.Text: These are S.G.514.518. Natural bridge. These are the two lowest values of the red cross airmail stamps of 1947 (S.G.338-339). Above the bridge the southern arm of the stream can be followed to its source at the Neba el-Lebn or milk Fountain.
